metadata.name: BR2B
metadata.description:
Gemara NFT is a distinct timepiece collection representative of the history and significance of the Babylonian Talmud, a set of central, ancient and foundational law texts compiled and established over
1,000 years ago. The generated layout of this collection mirrors that of the traditional layout of the Talmud and its structure. The intricate layouts are exact and true to the original format.
